featured.text: They flash a false response when these males signal overhead, but eat them when they land. 48.
The males fly overhead, flashing light from the undersides of their bodies.

definition.zh_def: 在頭頂上方的；高於某物的
definition.en_def: Located above the level of the head; in the upper part of a space.
definition.example: The overhead lights in the room were too bright for my eyes.
